  "body": "### Overview\r\n\r\nI'd like to be able to change the chain id from 1337 to 1 when running \r\n`brownie console --network mainnet-fork`\r\n\r\nIn general, I don't see how to change ganache cli settings when running mainnet-fork.\r\nI tried to set a config for 'mainnet-fork' under the networks config of `brownie-config.yaml` but didn't see the changes reflected.\r\n\r\n",
