    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Current solution has been to modify `network-config.yaml` found at `~/.brownie` in this way:\r\n\r\n```yaml\r\ndevelopment:\r\n  - name: Ganache-CLI (Mainnet Fork)\r\n    id: mainnet-fork\r\n    cmd: ganache-cli --chainId 1 --networkId 1 # <--- HERE\r\n    host: http://127.0.0.1\r\n    timeout: 120\r\n    cmd_settings:\r\n      port: 8545\r\n      gas_limit: 12000000\r\n      accounts: 10\r\n      evm_version: istanbul\r\n      mnemonic: brownie\r\n      fork: mainnet\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n",
